Frequently Asked Questions

Q: Can I use this for my personal projects?
A: Yes, without any restrictions or fees.

Q: Can I use this in my startup (under 10 people)?
A: Yes, without any restrictions or fees.

Q: Can my company (10+ employees) use this?
A: You need a commercial license for the original skill. Contact the Licensor.

Q: Can I fork and modify this for personal use?
A: Yes. You can modify it freely for personal and internal use.

Q: Can I fork and sell my modified version?
A: No. All derivative works must be open source and free. You cannot charge
   for any version derived from this skill.

Q: Can I fork, modify, and keep my version private?
A: No. Derivative works must be publicly available as open source.

Q: What happens on the Change Date (2030-04-27)?
A: The entire work becomes Apache 2.0 licensed. All restrictions are removed,
   including the derivative works requirement.
